---
layout: base.njk
title: SuperHappycat
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Hi, I'm SuperHappycat</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Curious about everything. Writing about what I find.</p>
</section>

<section class="home-section">
  <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
  <ul class="post-list">
  {%- for post in collections.post | reverse %}
    {%- if loop.index <= 3 %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    </li>
    {%- endif %}
  {%- endfor %}
  </ul>
  <p><a href="{{ '/blog/' | url }}">View all posts &rarr;</a></p>
</section>

<section class="home-section">
  <h2>What This Place Is</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>&lt;/&gt; Code</h3>
      <p>Projects, experiments, and things I've built or broken.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>&#9998; Writing</h3>
      <p>Stories, ideas, and creative experiments.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>&#127758; Discovery</h3>
      <p>This may actually just be a collection of whatever rabbit hole I fall into next.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
